item.dc:creator: @KeV KeV
item.description:
@KeV wrote:

The first error, obiously means you’ve deleted the song files (like me) because they have annoyed you lol. ‘Error downloading news’ comes up for me aswell, thats not a problem.

However, its saying your cache folder is gone (which should be in your Moparscape directory). It’s best just downloading moparscape again, and fully extracting the files in the folder.
